data.description: Under Construction. The Freeport floor plan features 1,499 square feet of living space with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a 2 car garage. This home is nicely appointed with stainless steel kitchen appliances including Refrigerator, 18" tile floors in the main living areas, carpeted bedrooms, washer/dryer, and a smart home package. The first bathroom features a large walk-in closet, and a walk-in shower (perfect for opposite schedules). This home is quality built with a full builder warranty and is conveniently located near shopping. Photographs, colors, features, and sizes are for illustration purposes only and will vary from the homes as built. Please note: this home has been permitted, started, and currently mid way through construction. The completion date is only an estimate. The sale price reflects a "move-in-ready" home, including lot. There is no bidding, there are no contract escalation clauses and, there is no need for a construction loan. For qualified buyers; the builder offers low down payment requirements, and closing cost assistance.
